You can improve security by adding salt and then taking sha256 (or whatever) . Salt is just random junk to improve security. Something like this

$salt = substr(str_pad(dechex(mt_rand()),8,'0',STR_PAD_LEFT),-8);
$secured = $salt . hash('sha256',$password.$salt);
